Package: fink-libcheck
Version: @VERSION@
Revision: @REVISION@
Source: %n-%v.tar
NoSourceDirectory: true
Depends: base-files
Essential: No
CompileScript: ./setup.sh %p
InstallScript: ./install.sh %i
#
Description: Lib checking utility for Fink installation
DescDetail: <<
Utility that allows you to check what files are linked against which
libraries version specific and no version.  The utility is mostly
useful for libaries that break backwards compatibility, enabaling you
to easily find the files that are linked against the older libs and
it will even collect a list and ask you if you want to rebuild them.
<<
